  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- this century has been the most violent century, beginning with the Turkish genocide of the Armenians in 1915 to 1919, all through these years-- Cambodia, Rwanda, Somalia, the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I would just stress, I have to say, the word 'education,' again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Become educated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I feel--.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and to-- to other people who have an opportunity to be fortunate enough to-- to go to a foreign country, where you really can get into the culture of other people around the world, wherever it is.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I always quote [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the philosopher, Spanish-born, Harvard-educated George Santayana, who wrote in 1905, 'those who cannot remember the past are condemned to repeat it.' And that we just have to remember the history of the past so that hopefully, we will not repeat it.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or if it is repeated, that we will not turn our heads and look the other way, as so many foreign heads of state, church leaders, and others did during this genocide.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we have to overcome these prejudices to structure our future with faith, hope, and international understanding, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] peace, and justice.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you, Gary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I appreciate your having been my interviewer, and I'm highly honored to even sit here in this position to tell my story from a different perspective, maybe even that of a survivor.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're welcome.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
